Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.13,0:00:45.05,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"11 Years Ago・(History)"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.09,0:00:53.01,Main,,0,0,0,,It smells nice. You smell it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.01,0:00:54.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Sniff, sniff.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.85,0:00:57.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, all set.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.35,0:00:59.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Everybody smile pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.40,0:01:04.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Say cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.90,0:01:15.20,Main,,0,0,0,,We hated you from the beginning--\Nand loved you from the beginning, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.20,0:01:18.83,Main,,0,0,0,,And so we wanted to\Nbecome true friends with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.83,0:01:21.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to cross the wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.54,0:01:24.08,Main,,0,0,0,,...and have you all to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.13,0:01:30.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurikumaaaaaaaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.26,0:01:31.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurikuma Arashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.14,0:01:38.60,Main,,0,0,0,,"I WANT TO HAVE YOU ALL TO MYSELF"\N{\i1}Viens avec moi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.60,0:01:41.89,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Church chimes echo in the distance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.89,0:01:44.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Offer up a prayer and betray today{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.73,0:01:50.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wander in a dark forest, then become{\i0}\N{\i1}the morning moon at the Wall of Severance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.23,0:01:52.82,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't join the Invisible Storm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.82,0:01:56.74,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once I've made you stickier{\i0}\N{\i1}with sweet, thin honey{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.74,0:02:01.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please, approve me, I'll be a good girl{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.00,0:02:06.92,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Picture-book pages dancing on{\i0}\N{\i1}the breeze shake up shadowy memories{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.63,0:02:12.63,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Always{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.51,0:02:18.85,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be waiting you-know-where,{\i0}\N{\i1}in an empty world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.85,0:02:23.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if everything falls apart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:30.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you have to gracefully writhe,{\i0}\N{\i1}even if you have to bend space-time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.48,0:02:34.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Find me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.03,0:02:45.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Flower petals will slowly{\i0}\N{\i1}enfold us on a starry night{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.46,0:02:47.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.21,0:02:49.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.96,0:02:52.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.22,0:03:01.89,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}J'ai besoin de toi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.27,0:03:10.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Delicious smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:11.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Slurp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.78,0:03:19.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha, good morning, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:21.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.16,0:03:24.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko! Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.91,0:03:27.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.08,0:03:28.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Lick!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.50,0:03:34.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha, you're close to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.17,0:03:38.09,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:40.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.01,0:03:43.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you in my house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.85,0:03:45.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I moved in, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:46.31,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:50.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl! All finished moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:51.31,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.31,0:03:52.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:56.94,Main,,0,0,0,,We're your...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:58.53,Main,,0,0,0,,...new neighbors!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:06.83,Main,,0,0,0,,New-neighbor new-dles!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.83,0:04:08.29,Main,,0,0,0,,We're your...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:09.92,Main,,0,0,0,,...new neighbors!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:12.38,Main,,0,0,0,,New-neighbor new-dles!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.84,0:04:16.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Get... Get...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.01,0:04:18.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Get {\i1}out{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:26.06,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not acceptable to move in\Nwithout asking! I want you out today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.06,0:04:29.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl. But Kure-{\i1}chin{\i0}, you ate your noodles!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.73,0:04:33.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-That isn't the issue here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:36.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Look, it's that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:39.40,Main,,0,0,0,,The one who's bad luck to all her friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:46.75,Main,,0,0,0,,It's worse than bad luck! Girls are\Ngoing missing--and only from {\i1}her {\i0}class!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:49.25,Main,,0,0,0,,There you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.25,0:04:52.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Getting close to me is bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:56.17,Main,,0,0,0,,It's true. You'll get caught\Nup in the Invisible Storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:04:58.84,Main,,0,0,0,,The Invisible Storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:05:05.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. If you make friends with me,\Nyou'll be excluded. It's the law of this herd.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:10.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Now that you get it, just leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:17.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl! {\i1}You're {\i0}the one who doesn't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.94,0:05:21.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I told you, Ginko and I came\Nhere to make friends with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:25.28,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll protect Kureha from the Invisible Storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.28,0:05:29.16,Main,,0,0,0,,We won't back down on love, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.75,0:05:38.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying! There was a bear\Nmasquerading as human!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:39.92,Main,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.92,0:05:44.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Please believe me.\NYurizono really did turn into a bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:49.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurizono ate Sumika--I mean, Izumino.\NShe told me so herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.81,0:05:52.56,Main,,0,0,0,,So I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:06:01.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I looked right at her and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.78,0:06:03.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:05.45,Main,,0,0,0,,That's enough of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.45,0:06:06.78,Main,,0,0,0,,But Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.78,0:06:11.37,Main,,0,0,0,,You poor thing. The shock was too\Nmuch for you, and you hallucinated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:13.04,Main,,0,0,0,,No! It was--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.04,0:06:20.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't tell you to do it right away,\Nbut eventually you'll need to accept reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.93,0:06:29.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right--next Sunday\Nis your birthday, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:30.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.06,0:06:35.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Reia's little girl, about to\Nbe seventeen! Time certainly flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.23,0:06:37.52,Main,,0,0,0,,What would you like this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.52,0:06:41.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Dinner out? Or is there a present you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.32,0:06:43.53,Main,,0,0,0,,No, not this year...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.70,0:06:49.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, your mother's pendant...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.37,0:06:56.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I gave that pendant to her\Nfor her seventeenth birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.29,0:06:58.04,Main,,0,0,0,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:07:02.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. It was a symbol of our\Npromise between friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:05.76,Main,,0,0,0,,We pledged to never forget love.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.76,0:07:07.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Never forget love?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.59,0:07:13.22,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right. As long as you don't\Nforget love, you'll never be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:15.39,Main,,0,0,0,,If you don't give up on love,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:20.19,Main,,0,0,0,,even if you lose something,\Nyou'll never be invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.19,0:07:24.19,Main,,0,0,0,,But love does cause us pain sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.19,0:07:27.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Whenever we remember that lost time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:30.24,Main,,0,0,0,,That lost time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:32.37,Main,,0,0,0,,"Flashback"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:41.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.42,0:07:46.88,Main,,0,0,0,,When that happens, we try to focus on\Nsomething else and not be too hard on ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:52.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha, what you need\Nright now is a new friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:54.56,Main,,0,0,0,,A... new friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.56,0:07:58.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, someone who's not Izumino.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.19,0:07:59.40,Main,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:00.52,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:04.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want a new friend.\NSumika is my only friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:07.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll never give up on love!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:13.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl, growl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:22.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl. Kure-{\i1}chin{\i0}'s eating a {\i1}chikuwa {\i0}roll again?\NDoes it really smell that delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:24.75,Main,,0,0,0,,That's the taste of love for Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:26.09,Main,,0,0,0,,The taste of love?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:30.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, something no storm\Nor bear or human can destroy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:32.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you sure anything like that exists?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.72,0:08:34.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course. It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.39,0:09:08.88,Main,,0,0,0,,"Flashback"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:14.89,Main,,0,0,0,,It's okay, you're not alone. I'm your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.35,0:09:18.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:20.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Lady Kumaria...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.27,0:09:26.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I remember getting love from someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.23,0:09:30.70,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why I came here, across the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:33.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha, I want you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.41,0:09:36.08,Main,,0,0,0,,...all to myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:42.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.75,0:09:46.75,MainTop,,0,0,0,,Do you have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.09,0:09:52.17,Main,,0,0,0,,We all talked it over this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:58.60,Main,,0,0,0,,We were wrong.\NWe think we've been really cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.60,0:10:01.60,Main,,0,0,0,,So we want to make amends!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.89,0:10:05.40,Main,,0,0,0,,To you... and to Izumino.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.40,0:10:06.90,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.23,0:10:09.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:14.86,Main,,0,0,0,,You people excluded Sumika!\NYou don't have the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:18.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Why the change of heart now?\NIf you're playing a game, play it to the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:24.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't lose to people like you.\NYou won't make me invisible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.58,0:10:29.92,Main,,0,0,0,,W-We're sorry! We've been so awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:31.76,Main,,0,0,0,,We're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.39,0:10:39.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Only we get to make friends with Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:43.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Girls in our way big time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:46.23,Main,,0,0,0,,...get eaten by bears, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:53.61,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Yuri Store"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:10:55.03,MainTop,,0,0,0,,Growl...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.03,0:11:01.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's see. "Article 1: The way to\Na girl's heart is through her stomach."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:02.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.87,0:11:07.46,Main,,0,0,0,,You and I gotta make Kure-{\i1}chin {\i0}a\Nflavor she loves as much as {\i1}chikuwa {\i0}rolls!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.46,0:11:11.59,Main,,0,0,0,,And {\i1}then{\i0}... Muahaha, I'm so clever!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.38,0:11:15.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Delicious smell, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.72,0:11:20.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko! You can't transform here,\Nno matter how hungry you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.10,0:11:25.14,Main,,0,0,0,,We're only allowed to eat\Nthe flesh of invisible girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:27.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Grooowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.73,0:11:30.48,Main,,0,0,0,,So, what foods does Kure-{\i1}chin {\i0}like?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:33.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shiokara {\i0}and spaghetti.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.03,0:11:35.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't that sort of old-man-ish?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:37.53,Main,,0,0,0,,She's liked them since she was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.53,0:11:41.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm, then tonight's dinner will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.62,0:11:42.87,Main,,0,0,0,,"All for Kureha"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:50.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl! Welcome home, Kure-{\i1}chin{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:52.25,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:54.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Dinner, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.09,0:11:58.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Heehee, we're making your love flavor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:12:01.05,Main,,0,0,0,,My... "love flavor"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.89,0:12:05.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Yep, your two favorites!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:07.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-You can't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.89,0:12:14.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes! We call it "Shiokara Spaghetti"!\NDelicious smell, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:19.95,Main,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, wow! A flavor pairing made in heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.95,0:12:23.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Here, Ginko, a cherry tomato. Say "ah"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:25.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:30.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Here, Ginko, creamy honey flan. Say "ah"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.13,0:12:31.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:36.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Here, Ginko, creamy lightly\Nsalted salmon. Say "ah"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.76,0:12:38.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.05,0:12:42.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Now it's your turn, growl! Say "ah"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:44.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.43,0:12:45.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:55.73,Main,,0,0,0,,--But... but... you like {\i1}shiokara {\i0}and spaghetti!\N--Mm-hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.73,0:12:57.49,Main,,0,0,0,,How did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.49,0:12:59.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.49,0:13:05.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I only ever told Sumika that.\NYou transfer students wouldn't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.08,0:13:08.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm, I'm not sure how!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:10.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I told you to stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.91,0:13:15.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl! But we want to be your friends--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.09,0:13:16.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:20.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Enough about "friends"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.22,0:13:23.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Why is everyone trying to\Nmake me give up on my love?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:28.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want any new friends.\NSumika is my only friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:33.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Sumika is my only love!\NI don't want anything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:37.02,Main,,0,0,0,,What's {\i1}with {\i0}you two?!\NWhy do you want to get close to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.24,0:13:42.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl. I was super scared back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.91,0:13:48.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought you were about\Nto tell Kure-{\i1}chin {\i0}the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:53.25,Main,,0,0,0,,But if you tell her,\Nwe can't be human girls anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.25,0:13:55.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Those are the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.84,0:14:00.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, I hope she remembers you soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:04.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Here I am, Ginko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:10.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.14,0:14:14.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I was happy, but I just couldn't admit it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.61,0:14:19.86,Main,,0,0,0,,It's okay, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:23.95,Main,,0,0,0,,So I was thinking,\Nif we washed each other all over,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.95,0:14:26.91,Main,,0,0,0,,we could really get to know each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.41,0:14:29.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Gorgeous smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:36.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Does that feel good, Ginko?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:38.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:42.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Does this spot feel good too, Ginko?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.13,0:14:45.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's... good too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:50.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Does this spot feel {\i1}really {\i0}good, Ginko?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:57.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's... really... good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.23,0:15:01.86,Main,,0,0,0,,There, all clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.37,0:15:10.91,Main,,0,0,0,,"Happy Birthday Kureha"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.16,0:15:12.12,Main,,0,0,0,,"From Sumika"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:16.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Here, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.75,0:15:18.38,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Flashback"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.42,0:15:19.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I know it's a little early...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:20.34,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"One Month Ago・(History)"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.34,0:15:23.13,MainTop,,0,0,0,,My birthday isn't for a while, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:28.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I know. But I have to give you this today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.05,0:15:29.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh? You're so weird, Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.89,0:15:32.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait! Don't open it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.56,0:15:33.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:38.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I want you to read it here on your birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.19,0:15:39.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.36,0:15:42.19,Main,,0,0,0,,It's my present to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.19,0:15:43.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Present?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.49,0:15:48.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Please? You'll understand when you read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.57,0:15:49.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.95,0:15:51.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Listen, Kureha...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:57.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I want you to always smile like that, like a flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.92,0:16:00.59,Main,,0,0,0,,That's my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.59,0:16:04.42,Main,,0,0,0,,So I'd be happy even just\Nwatching you from a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:08.84,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NI'm always by your side, Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:14.06,Main,,0,0,0,,That's true... You didn't back down on love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:17.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll never, never forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.27,0:16:18.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Sumika?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.15,0:16:23.73,Main,,0,0,0,,They'll bloom soon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:25.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.99,0:16:30.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Sumika, you're my only friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.91,0:16:38.66,Main,,0,0,0,,The flowerbed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:44.96,Main,,0,0,0,,We asked the school to make it\Nso you could grow flowers here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:47.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry about yesterday. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.13,0:16:53.43,Main,,0,0,0,,The Invisible Storm wrecked\Nthis place, and we want to fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.43,0:16:59.69,Main,,0,0,0,,We want to fill it with flowers,\Nand make Izumino's last wish come true...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:02.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Sumika's last wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.44,0:17:06.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. Next Sunday is your birthday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:08.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.65,0:17:14.78,Main,,0,0,0,,See, I heard that a little while\Nbefore that happened to Izumino...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.78,0:17:16.24,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:22.25,Main,,0,0,0,,...she said she wanted to celebrate\Nyour birthday in a garden full of flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:24.84,Main,,0,0,0,,It's my present to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.05,0:17:28.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Sumika...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.76,0:17:33.35,Main,,0,0,0,,We want you to let {\i1}us {\i0}celebrate your birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:36.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Because that's what Izumino wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:42.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Please--for Izumino's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:18:02.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl! What's with that?!\NYou and I are her friends, not them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.75,0:18:04.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Right, Ginko?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.80,0:18:13.59,Main,,0,0,0,,We don't have much time before Tsubaki's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:15.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's start today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:17.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:43.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone, thank you for\Nworking hard these past few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.29,0:18:43.87,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Exclusion Ceremony・(Exclusion)"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.87,0:18:45.58,MainTop,,0,0,0,,Thanks to your efforts,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.58,0:18:49.55,MainTop,,0,0,0,,Kureha Tsubaki has started to\Nbelieve that we are her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.55,0:18:52.05,Main,,0,0,0,,We just need to endure a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.05,0:18:56.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, let's confirm our feelings one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.51,0:18:59.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Who is the evil we must exclude?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.14,0:19:01.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's search evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.64,0:19:04.85,Main,,0,0,0,,"5. Hinako Serina"\N"6. Uchiko Ai"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.85,0:19:06.02,Main,,0,0,0,,"4. Saori Shimabukuro"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.02,0:19:07.19,Main,,0,0,0,,"3. Aoi Uezu"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:09.48,Main,,0,0,0,,"2. Karen Tanaka"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:11.11,Main,,0,0,0,,"1. Evil = Kureha Tsubaki"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:12.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Select!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.28,0:19:16.45,Main,,0,0,0,,We have chosen Kureha Tsubaki as the evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.45,0:19:18.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Grrrrrrr...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.24,0:19:20.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl. This is great, Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:25.33,Main,,0,0,0,,She {\i1}is {\i0}an invisible girl.\NThis means we can eat her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:28.42,Main,,0,0,0,,The time for judgment has come, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.05,0:19:31.00,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Convening Yuri Trial・(Trial)"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:34.21,MainTop,,0,0,0,,We now begin the Yuri Trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.21,0:19:40.51,MainTop,,0,0,0,,I want to eat her. I'll save\NKureha from the Invisible Storm, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.51,0:19:42.10,Main,,0,0,0,,This again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.10,0:19:46.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Doesn't everyone want to protect\Nthe girl they love? Sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:48.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be too sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.44,0:19:54.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Defendant-bears, you've eaten several\Nhumans affiliated with the Invisible Storm
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.11,0:19:59.32,Main,,0,0,0,,in the name of "saving\NKureha Tsubaki," haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.32,0:20:00.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.41,0:20:02.41,Main,,0,0,0,,You're guilty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.41,0:20:07.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko Yurishiro, answer honestly:\Nwhat is it that you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.96,0:20:11.21,Main,,0,0,0,,"Saving Kureha Tsubaki" is an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.21,0:20:13.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't it true that all you {\i1}really {\i0}want
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:17.26,Main,,0,0,0,,is to make yourself\NKureha Tsubaki's only friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.26,0:20:22.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Objection! The prosecutor is\Nspeculating based on his personal sadism!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.18,0:20:26.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Ginko only wants to give\Nback the love she got from Kure-{\i1}chin{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.27,0:20:28.60,Main,,0,0,0,,She only wants a Promise Kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.44,0:20:33.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Order! Objection overruled.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.90,0:20:38.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko Yurishiro, please answer\Nthe prosecutor's question.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.74,0:20:43.08,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right. I want to\Nhave Kureha all to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.08,0:20:43.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.91,0:20:47.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to be friends with\NKureha again. I want her love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.75,0:20:53.04,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why I crossed the wall,\Nand dragged Lulu into it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.04,0:20:55.55,Main,,0,0,0,,No, I wanted to--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.55,0:21:01.22,Main,,0,0,0,,But I still won't back down on love!\NI'll do whatever I have to for love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.22,0:21:07.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll do anything. There's no going\Nback now--I've committed a serious crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.56,0:21:10.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko? What "serious crime"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.81,0:21:11.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.90,0:21:15.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa! No need to finish that sentence, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.69,0:21:19.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Your Honor, the defendant-bear\Njust confessed to a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:23.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Please find her guilty at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:31.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko Yurishiro, is your love the real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.42,0:21:32.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.58,0:21:40.22,Main,,0,0,0,,And if it's an egotistical love?\NIf that pride destroys you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.22,0:21:43.22,Main,,0,0,0,,That's fine. I'm a criminal-bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.22,0:21:49.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I see. Defendant-bears, will you\Nbe invisible? Or will you eat humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.85,0:21:51.77,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.77,0:21:53.10,Main,,0,0,0,,...humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.10,0:21:54.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.94,0:21:58.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I now declare the verdict.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.36,0:22:00.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuri approved!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.49,0:22:08.58,Main,,0,0,0,,What did you want? It's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.58,0:22:12.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl. Ginko and I are going to\Nbe friends with Kure-{\i1}chin{\i0}, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.92,0:22:15.46,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.46,0:22:17.34,Main,,0,0,0,,We won't let you have your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.34,0:22:19.84,Main,,0,0,0,,In other words, disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.84,0:22:23.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.13,0:22:24.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Bear shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.76,0:22:29.97,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you two? A-Are you--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.97,0:22:32.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl! We're bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.56,0:22:35.06,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll eat you up, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.06,0:22:38.40,Main,,0,0,0,,N-No! S-Someone help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.70,0:22:48.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.74,0:22:53.83,Main,,0,0,0,,One bear successfully eliminated by our trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.83,0:22:56.96,Main,,0,0,0,,We know what you two really are!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.22,0:23:07.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.78,0:23:31.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the boundary that severed{\i0}\N{\i1}ripe moon from sleeping forest{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.79,0:23:38.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Break the law God shackles us with and smile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.46,0:23:45.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I turned away from the bleating flock{\i0}\N{\i1}of shadows and howled my bloodthirsty ego{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.51,0:23:52.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here amidst the Invisible Storm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.10,0:23:55.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Overflowing honey and soul{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.48,0:23:58.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to rend silk with my fangs{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.94,0:24:05.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm afraid you'll vanish{\i0}\N{\i1}like the world's last ray of hope{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.99,0:24:12.83,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The savage beast inside me{\i0}\N{\i1}tore out the throat of innocence{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.83,0:24:22.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on, shoot me through the heart{\i0}\N{\i1}with your sweet-scented Barrett of love{\i0}
